formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
Note-1: The Loan taken from SBI is for the commercial project known as "The Millenium". Land has been mortgaged for such loan. Such loan is also used for incurring the expenditure of the said project only. The project "The Millenium Gloria" is also situated on the same land and thus even though loan is not taken for such project, the units of "The Millennium Gloria" come under the purview of the loan taken for the project "The Millenium". While selling units of "The Millenium Gloria", NOC has to be obtained from the loan sanctioning bank.
Note:2
Office No. 25, 26 and 43 does not created agreement for sale, The promoter and allotees desided directly created sale deed.
